{"parentUuid":"69197ebc-e35a-42c8-94d2-82c5f31c1bd5","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/kokiyoshida/Knowhere-inc/stripe-link","sessionId":"e0bc884b-355a-464e-98ff-5781a828a10b","version":"2.0.5","gitBranch":"fix/default-extended-zoom-type","message":{"id":"msg_01BJfgLgxmE5r7sMbzPhPUsx","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`lib/controllers/camera_controller.dart` を確認しました。\n\nデフォルトの `extendedZoomType` は **`null`** です。\n\n具体的には：\n\n1. **初期状態（`build()` メソッド）**: `lib/controllers/camera_controller.dart:261`\n   ```dart\n   extendedZoom: null,\n   ```\n\n2. **`setCameraModeAuto()` メソッド内で決定**: `lib/controllers/camera_controller.dart:1310-1314`\n   ```dart\n   final savedExtendedZoomType = profileStorage.getCameraExtendedZoomType();\n   final extendedZoomType = savedExtendedZoomType ??\n       (state.isTelephotoAvailable == true\n           ? ExtendedZoomType.zoom\n           : ExtendedZoomType.wide);\n   ```\n\nつまり、カメラ初期化時は `null` で、`setCameraModeAuto()` 実行時に：\n- 保存された設定があればそれを使用\n- なければ望遠レンズ利用可能なら `ExtendedZoomType.zoom`\n- 望遠レンズ不可なら `ExtendedZoomType.wide`\n\nが設定されます。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":40921,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":40921,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":331,"service_tier":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"b6a4d4ab-0bbb-4b69-82d3-e81fbc565fff","timestamp":"2025-10-03T03:00:35.554Z"}
